                                        <h3 class="recommended-reads__item__title">
                                            You Are the Product                                        </h3>
                                        <p class="recommended-reads__item__excerpt">
                                            Like pretty much everyone who uses the internet, I have seen many terrible things that I did not search for and that I cannot unsee. <br> <br>

Rosanna McLaughlin on what the internet thinks she wants.                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </a>
