          <div class="col-12 col-md-8 flex --direction-col --justify-content-center article-contributor-main">
            <div class="article-contributor__meta-container">
              <h1 class="article-contributor-section_title">Xiao Hai</h1>
              <p class="article-contributor-section_content">Xiao Hai is a Shangqiu- born, Beijing-based poet. His works have appeared in <em>World Literature Today</em> and <em>Chinese Literature Today</em>. His debut anthology, <em>Sisyphus on the Wenyu River</em>, is forthcoming in 2025.</p>
              <a class="article-contributor-section_link" href="https://granta.com/xiao-hai">More about the author </a>
            </div>
